metadata.name: Target Practice
metadata.description:
A refreshing day at the pool. 

1 Malibu pool, 3 bottles of champagne, and 1 roll of medium format film come together in glamorous fashion to create one of my classic high-life images.

The winner of "Target Practice" will also be awarded a second image from this shoot as an edition of 10 minted on a separate contract. The collector will be able to keep, sell, give away, or burn these editions at their discretion. But one (1) edition must remain in their wallet indefinitely or until they sell "Target Practice".
